    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project car or a no-frills way to get from point A to point B? This vehicle is priced to reflect its current condition \u2014 it shows significant wear both inside and out, and has some mechanical issues that will need attention. That said, it's a great opportunity for a handy buyer or someone looking for an affordable fixer-upper! Grab it at a price that leaves room in your budget for the work it needs.",
      "price": 5500.0,
