      "description": "This car is in poor condition. It has significant mechanical issues that will require attention and may affect reliability. The exterior shows noticeable damage including scratches, dents, and possible rust or paint deterioration. The interior is worn with visible damage to surfaces and components. This car may be suitable for someone willing to invest in repairs, but it should not be expected to perform like a well-maintained vehicle.",
      "price": 5500.0,
